该模板生成[[Google学术搜索|Google Scholar]]上人物主页的链接。

== Usage ==
One parameter:
: <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | ''ID'' }}</code>
: <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id= ''ID'' }}</code>

Two parameters:
: <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | ''ID'' | ''NAME'' }}</code>
: <code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id= ''ID'' | name= ''NAME'' }}</code>

== Examples ==

===One parameter===
This parameter will be the ID string used in the [[统一资源定位符|URL]] at Google Scholar. When one parameter is used, the [[锚文本|link text]] is the title of the Wikipedia article where the template is used.

''URL:''
: <kbd><nowiki>https://</nowiki>scholar.google.com/citations?user={{hilite|EeTd0CYAAAAJ}}</kbd>
''Usage:''
: <code><nowiki>* {{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | EeTd0CYAAAAJ }}</code>
: <code><nowiki>* {{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id= EeTd0CYAAAAJ }}</code>
''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}} | EeTd0CYAAAAJ }}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id= EeTd0CYAAAAJ }}

[The name of the Wikipedia page you now are looking at is displayed above. The lead name will change according to the name of the Wikipedia page the template is used on.]

===Two parameters===
The first parameter will be the ID string used in the [[统一资源定位符|URL]] at Google Scholar. The second parameter will be used at the [[锚文本|link text]].

''URL:''
: <kbd><nowiki>https://</nowiki>scholar.google.com/citations?user={{hilite|EeTd0CYAAAAJ}}</kbd>
''Usage:''
: <code><nowiki>* {{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | EeTd0CYAAAAJ | Yoelle Maarek }}</code>
: <code><nowiki>* {{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id= EeTd0CYAAAAJ | name= Yoelle Maarek }}</code>
''Output:''
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}} | EeTd0CYAAAAJ| Yoelle Maarek }}
:* {{{{BASEPAGENAME}} | id= EeTd0CYAAAAJ | name= Yoelle Maarek }}

=== No parameters and Wikidata property not defined ===
''Usage:''
: <code><nowiki>* {{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code>
''Output:''
:* {{ {{BASEPAGENAME}} }}

